author: IGN
description:
Being an Xbox fan can be a frustrating, depressing, weird, and occasionally shocking experience, but you can safely say that Xbox's previous year didn't lead to any dull moments. So, what will Xbox bring in 2026? 

A console/PC hybrid? Exciting new entries in Halo, Gears of War, Fable and Forza? Exclusives might be dead, but great games are plentiful, and in our video covering what to expect from Xbox in 2026, we'll be covering both the awesome and potentially terrible.

#IGN #Xbox #2026Games
title: What to Expect From Xbox in 2026

author: IGN
description:
Stranger Things wraps up it's pop culture dominating run with the finale of season 5. Dropping on New Year's Eve, the plucky heroes of Hawkins square off against Vecna one last time to save no less than the entire world! Can Eleven, Mike, Will, Dustin and Lucas defeat their Upside Down nemesis? More importantly, can series creators The Duffer Brothers stick the landing after the truly remarkable run? IGN's reviewer Tara Bennett shares her thoughts on how to kill characters in finales, why this final episode has shades of The Lord of the Rings: Return of the King and how expensive needle drops can be.

#IGN #StrangerThings #Netflix
title: Stranger Things Season 5 Finale Review

author: IGN
description: Take a look at the 0.2 Update Launch Trailer for Assetto Corsa Rally, a high-fidelity racing simulation game developed by Supernova Games Studios. Players can now access a new update for the game, bringing snowy and iced surfaces with the new scenario set in Livigno (Italian Alps), a new and legendary Rally car, overall bug fixes, and performance improvements. The 0.2 Update for Assetto Corsa Rally is available for PC (Steam).
title: Assetto Corsa Rally - Official 0.2 Update Launch Trailer
